@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tehyqn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = (v2 - (v0 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.88)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.68) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.56)) * (0.64 / wp.abs(v0 + 0.75)))
    tmp = 0.65
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.01) * (v2 + 0.84 + tmp + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
